    SELECT TOP(2) [a].[Id], [a].[Address], [a].[AttractionTypes], [a].[Author], [a].[AuthorId], [a].[AvgRates], [a].[Contact], [a].[CreateDate], [a].[Currency], [a].[DefaultExperienceId], [a].[DefaultGalleryId], [a].[DefaultName], [a].[Description], [a].[DestinationId], [a].[FromExperience], [a].[Latitude], [a].[Longitude], [a].[MapImageUri], [a].[PriceFrom], [a].[Priority], [a].[PropertyGroups], [a].[RouteUri], [a].[Status], [a].[ThumbnailUrl], [a].[TotalComments], [a].[TotalLikes], [a].[TotalRates], [a].[TouristClasses], [a].[TouristObjects], [a].[VisitDuration], [a].[Website], [d].[Id] AS [Id0], [d].[AvgRates] AS [AvgRates0], [d].[BannerUrl], [d].[CityId], [d].[CityName], [d].[Continent], [d].[CountryId], [d].[CountryName], [d].[DefaultGalleryId] AS [DefaultGalleryId0], [d].[DefaultName] AS [DefaultName0], [d].[Description] AS [Description0], [d].[DestinationOverviewId], [d].[Latitude] AS [Latitude0], [d].[Longitude] AS [Longitude0], [d].[MapImageUri] AS [MapImageUri0], [d].[RouteUri] AS [RouteUri0], [d].[StateId], [d].[StateName], [d].[ThumbnailUrl] AS [ThumbnailUrl0], [d].[TotalLikes] AS [TotalLikes0], [d].[TotalRates] AS [TotalRates0]
    FROM [Attraction] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Destination] AS [d] ON [a].[DestinationId] = [d].[Id]
    WHERE [a].[Id] = @__p_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [AttractionLanguage] AS [a0] ON [t].[Id] = [a0].[AttractionId]
LEFT JOIN [AttractionTag] AS [a1] ON [t].[Id] = [a1].[AttractionId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [a0].[Id], [a1].[AttractionId], [a1].[TagId]" (0723d8ff)

""SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Address], [t].[AttractionTypes], [t].[Author], [t].[AuthorId], [t].[AvgRates], [t].[Contact], [t].[CreateDate], [t].[Currency], [t].[DefaultExperienceId], [t].[DefaultGalleryId], [t].[DefaultName], [t].[Description], [t].[DestinationId], [t].[FromExperience], [t].[Latitude], [t].[Longitude], [t].[MapImageUri], [t].[PriceFrom], [t].[Priority], [t].[PropertyGroups], [t].[RouteUri], [t].[Status], [t].[ThumbnailUrl], [t].[TotalComments], [t].[TotalLikes], [t].[TotalRates], [t].[TouristClasses], [t].[TouristObjects], [t].[VisitDuration], [t].[Website], [t].[Id0], [t].[AvgRates0], [t].[BannerUrl], [t].[CityId], [t].[CityName], [t].[Continent], [t].[CountryId], [t].[CountryName], [t].[DefaultGalleryId0], [t].[DefaultName0], [t].[Description0], [t].[DestinationOverviewId], [t].[Latitude0], [t].[Longitude0], [t].[MapImageUri0], [t].[RouteUri0], [t].[StateId], [t].[StateName], [t].[ThumbnailUrl0], [t].[TotalLikes0], [t].[TotalRates0], [a0].[Id], [a0].[AttractionId], [a0].[Description], [a0].[LangCode], [a0].[Name], [a1].[AttractionId], [a1].[TagId]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(2) [a].[Id], [a].[Address], [a].[AttractionTypes], [a].[Author], [a].[AuthorId], [a].[AvgRates], [a].[Contact], [a].[CreateDate], [a].[Currency], [a].[DefaultExperienceId], [a].[DefaultGalleryId], [a].[DefaultName], [a].[Description], [a].[DestinationId], [a].[FromExperience], [a].[Latitude], [a].[Longitude], [a].[MapImageUri], [a].[PriceFrom], [a].[Priority], [a].[PropertyGroups], [a].[RouteUri], [a].[Status], [a].[ThumbnailUrl], [a].[TotalComments], [a].[TotalLikes], [a].[TotalRates], [a].[TouristClasses], [a].[TouristObjects], [a].[VisitDuration], [a].[Website], [d].[Id] AS [Id0], [d].[AvgRates] AS [AvgRates0], [d].[BannerUrl], [d].[CityId], [d].[CityName], [d].[Continent], [d].[CountryId], [d].[CountryName], [d].[DefaultGalleryId] AS [DefaultGalleryId0], [d].[DefaultName] AS [DefaultName0], [d].[Description] AS [Description0], [d].[DestinationOverviewId], [d].[Latitude] AS [Latitude0], [d].[Longitude] AS [Longitude0], [d].[MapImageUri] AS [MapImageUri0], [d].[RouteUri] AS [RouteUri0], [d].[StateId], [d].[StateName], [d].[ThumbnailUrl] AS [ThumbnailUrl0], [d].[TotalLikes] AS [TotalLikes0], [d].[TotalRates] AS [TotalRates0]
    FROM [Attraction] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Destination] AS [d] ON [a].[DestinationId] = [d].[Id]
    WHERE [a].[Id] = @__p_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [AttractionLanguage] AS [a0] ON [t].[Id] = [a0].[AttractionId]
